    • withDimension

      public FieldType.Builder withDimension(Integer dimension)
      Specifies the number of dimensions of the vector embeddings in this field. This applies only to FLOAT_VECTOR or BINARY_VECTOR fields.
      参数:
      dimension - A number of dimension is a positive integer ranging from 1 to 32768.
      返回:
      The builder object itself.

    • withMaxLength

      public FieldType.Builder withMaxLength(Integer maxLength)
      Specifies the maximum length of a string in this field. This applies only to VARCHAR fields.
      参数:
      maxLength - The maximum length of a field value is a positive integer ranging from 1 to 255.
      返回:
      The builder object itself.

    • withAutoID

      public FieldType.Builder withAutoID(boolean autoID)
      Specifies whether the primary key automatically increments as entities being inserted.
      参数:
      autoID - A true value indicates that a primary key will be added and it automatically increments. In this case, you do not need to use withPrimaryKey(boolean) manually specified a primary field.
